    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“这里无法用逻辑解释。记录，并且生存。”</h2>成为 Async Corp.（下称 背房公司） 的实验体，探索隐藏在穿墙（Noclip）现象背后的未知空间——“后室（Backrooms）”。<br>你的任务很简单：拍摄异常现象，并在努力生存的同时传输数据。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/8b2b25020b0bf91b36afa24bda2f2a80.poster.avif?t=1765500475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/8b2b25020b0bf91b36afa24bda2f2a80.webm?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/8b2b25020b0bf91b36afa24bda2f2a80.mp4?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>2025年7月30日 正式上线：更深入的探索</strong><br>探索范围现已超越酒店、泳池和停车场，继续深入到散发恶臭的“下水道”和诡异的“学校”。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>探索模式</u>：在不断变化的地形中直面迷失的恐惧。<br></li><li><u>故事模式</u>：沿着固定地图前进，揭开背房公司隐藏的巨大阴谋。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/c83cd12c598b6a07579268db7e87f63d.poster.avif?t=1765500475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/c83cd12c598b6a07579268db7e87f63d.webm?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010460/extras/c83cd12c598b6a07579268db7e87f63d.mp4?t=1765500475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>核心玩法：拍摄即生存</strong><br>收集散落在房间中的奇异物品，拍摄未知实体并留下记录。<br>拍摄到的数据既是你的生存分数，也是逃离的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span>{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/De<br>",
